text: Princess Rajwa Al Hussein (; born Rajwa Al Saif; 28 April 1994) is a Saudi member of the Jordanian royal family. She is married to Hussein, Crown Prince of Jordan, heir apparent to the Jordanian throne. The couple's engagement was announced in August 2022. They married in a ceremony in Amman on 1 June 2023. It was announced on 10 April 2024 that she and Hussein were expecting their first baby that summer. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:People from Riyadh Category:Jordanian princes and princesses
title: Princess Rajwa Al Hussein
